{"type":"text","timestamp":1775850521795,"sessionID":"ses_28711a618ffe3Venx6ULlhg9No","part":{"id":"prt_d78eff7af001LC5KWc9fm1hWhe","messageID":"msg_d78efdd1b001HpaFJb8vr5nv7e","sessionID":"ses_28711a618ffe3Venx6ULlhg9No","type":"text","text":"Now I have a comprehensive understanding of the codebase. Let me compile the verification report:\n\n## Verification Report: AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理\n\n### Module: pkg/workloadmanager (Go)\n### Project: agentcube\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Category | Status | Notes |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| **API Types** | ✅ PASS | AgentRuntime & CodeInterpreter properly defined |\n| **Tests** | ✅ PASS | All tests passing (40+ test cases) |\n| **client-go Generated Code** | ❌ **MISSING** | No clientset generated |\n| **Lifecycle Management Types** | ✅ PASS | Comprehensive lifecycle types defined |\n\n---\n\n## Detailed Verification\n\n### 1. API Group Configuration ✅\n\n**Spec Requirement:** `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh / v1alpha1`\n\n**Implementation:**\n```go\n// pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go\nSchemeGroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{\n    Group:   \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n    Version: \"v1alpha1\",\n}\n```\n\n**Constants verified:**\n- `APIGroup = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"` ✅\n- `APIVersion = \"v1alpha1\"` ✅\n- `FullAPIVersion = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\"` ✅\n\n### 2. CRD Types ✅\n\n#### AgentRuntime\n- **Kind:** `AgentRuntime` ✅\n- **REST Resource:** `agentruntimes` ✅ (via kubebuilder annotation `path=agentruntimes`)\n- **Short Names:** `ar`, `ars` ✅\n- **Subresource:** `status` ✅\n- **genclient annotation:** `+genclient` / `+genclient:noStatus` ✅\n\n#### CodeInterpreter\n- **Kind:** `CodeInterpreter` ✅\n- **REST Resource:** `codeinterpreters` ✅ (via kubebuilder annotation `path=codeinterpreters`)\n- **Short Names:** `ci`, `cis` ✅\n- **Subresource:** `status` ✅\n- **genclient annotation:** `+genclient` / `+genclient:noStatus` ✅\n\n### 3. API Type Methods ✅\n\n**AgentRuntime:**\n- `DeepCopy()` ✅\n- `DeepCopyInto()` ✅\n- `DeepCopyObject()` ✅\n\n**AgentRuntimeList:**\n- `DeepCopy()` ✅\n- `DeepCopyInto()` ✅\n- `DeepCopyObject()` ✅\n\n**CodeInterpreter & CodeInterpreterList:** Same methods ✅\n\n### 4. Lifecycle Management Types ✅\n\n**Location:** `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle/types.go`\n\n| Type | Status | Description |\n|------|--------|-------------|\n| `LifecycleManager` interface | ✅ | Complete with 12 methods |\n| `ResourceDeleter` interface | ✅ | Complete with 5 methods |\n| `DeletionMode` | ✅ | graceful, force, orphan |\n| `LifecyclePhase` | ✅ | 6 phases defined |\n| `DeletionReason` | ✅ | 6 reasons defined |\n| `SandboxResource` | ✅ | Resource metadata struct |\n| `SandboxState` | ✅ | State tracking struct |\n| `DeletionRequest` | ✅ | Deletion parameters |\n| `DeletionResult` | ✅ | Deletion outcome |\n| `TTLConfig` / `TTLStatus` | ✅ | TTL management |\n\n### 5. Missing Implementation ❌\n\n#### client-go Generated Files\n**Expected (per spec):** `clientset/versioned/**`\n\n**Missing files:**\n- `clientset/versioned/clientset.go` - `Interface` and `Clientset` struct\n- `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go` - `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\n- `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` - `AgentRuntimesGetter` / `AgentRuntimeInterface`\n- `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` - `CodeInterpretersGetter` / `CodeInterpreterInterface`\n- `clientset/versioned/scheme` - Scheme definitions\n\n### 6. Test Results ✅\n\n```bash\n# API Type Tests: ALL PASS\nTestAgentRuntimePhaseValues           PASS\nTestAgentRuntimeConditionTypeValues   PASS\nTestAgentRuntimeSpec                  PASS (13 sub-tests)\nTestAgentRuntimeStatus                PASS (6 sub-tests)\nTestAgentRuntimeCondition             PASS\nTestAgentRuntime                      PASS\nTestAgentRuntimeList                  PASS\nTestAgentRuntimeDeepCopy              PASS\nTestAgentRuntimeListDeepCopy          PASS\nTestAgentRuntimeSpecDeepCopy          PASS\nTestAgentRuntimeStatusDeepCopy        PASS\nTestAgentRuntimeConditionDeepCopy     PASS\nTestAgentRuntimeJSONMarshal           PASS\nTestAgentRuntimeListJSONMarshal       PASS\nTestDeepCopyObject                    PASS\nTestSchemeBuilder                     PASS\nTestResource                          PASS\nTestProtocolTypeValues                PASS\nTestAuthModeTypeValues                PASS\nTestTargetPort                        PASS\nTestCodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate    PASS\nTestCodeInterpreterSpec               PASS\nTestCodeInterpreterConditionTypeValues PASS\nTestCodeInterpreterCondition          PASS\nTestCodeInterpreterStatus             PASS\nTestCodeInterpreter                   PASS\nTestCodeInterpreterList               PASS\nTestCodeInterpreterDeepCopy           PASS\nTestCodeInterpreterListDeepCopy       PASS\nTestCodeInterpreterSpecDeepCopy       PASS\nTestCodeInterpreterStatusDeepCopy     PASS\nTestCodeInterpreterConditionDeepCopy  PASS\nTestCodeInterpreterSandboxTemplateDeepCopy PASS\nTestTargetPortDeepCopy                PASS\nTestCodeInterpreterJSONMarshal        PASS\nTestCodeInterpreterListJSONMarshal    PASS\nTestCodeInterpreterDeepCopyObject     PASS\n```\n\n### 7. Code Quality ✅\n\n- Proper copyright headers ✅\n- Consistent naming conventions ✅\n- Kubebuilder annotations present ✅\n- JSON tags properly defined ✅\n- DeepCopy generated via controller-gen ✅\n\n---\n\n## Conclusion\n\n| Aspect | Status |\n|--------|--------|\n| API Type Definitions | ✅ Complete |\n| Lifecycle Types | ✅ Complete |\n| Constants & Enums | ✅ Complete |\n| DeepCopy Generation | ✅ Complete |\n| Unit Tests | ✅ All Passing |\n| **client-go Generation** | ❌ **Missing** |\n\n### Required Actions\n\n1. **Generate client-go code** using `client-gen` or `controller-gen` to create:\n   - `clientset/versioned/` - Main clientset\n   - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/` - Typed clients\n   - `clientset/versioned/scheme/` - Scheme definitions\n\n2. **Generate informers and listers** (optional but recommended for controllers)\n\n### Recommendation\n\nThe codebase has solid API type definitions and comprehensive lifecycle management types. The main gap is the **generated client-go code**, which should be produced using the Kubernetes code generation tools. All existing tests pass successfully.","time":{"start":1775850521792,"end":1775850521792}}}
